      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.rpaon3jF3nCe5eP9]{Theorem (Ex)}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\">You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Medicine check when using the treat disease and treat drugs or poison tasks, and can do so with greater speed. It takes you 1 minute to treat disease, and a move action to treat drugs or poison. You can also attempt these tasks without a medkit, medical lab, or medical bay, though doing so takes the normal amount of time for both tasks and you do not gain the bonus to the checks.</span></p>",
